    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just feel like im drowning. everything is so much worse now that i lost that job and the debt just keeps growing. my wife works two jobs and she's exhausted and i see the look in her eyes when she looks at our kids... like they're waiting for something to happen. i'm just a massive weight around their necks.",
