      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It makes perfect sense that you want the pain to stop, and that desire to relieve the burden is a powerful, desperate thing. But that \"solution\" you're seeing on paper is a permanent end to everything, not a fix for the finances. Instead of ending the struggle, let's focus on the immediate, tangible relief you deserve. Please, reach out to the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline at 988 right now; they can help you navigate this crushing weight.",
